videos.description: Braian Angola bounces a pass to Terance Mann who jams it in the first half against Charleston Southern.
videos.headline: Florida State's Angola finds Mann for vicious dunk

videos.description: Travis McConico stays behind the line to knock in a few nice 3-pointers in the first half against Florida State.
videos.headline: Charleston Southern's  McConico drains 3 triples

videos.description: Terance Man finds Phil Cofer who gets past defenders and finishes with a one-handed slam in the first half.
videos.headline: Florida State's Cofer gets aggressive

videos.description: Terance Man finds Ike Obiagu in transition and he finishes with a mean dunk in the second half against Charleston Southern.
videos.headline: Florida State's Obiagu elevates for alley-oop

videos.description: Terance Mann throws a hard pass to Phil Cofer who steps behind the line and drains a 3-pointer in the second half.
videos.headline: Mann's tough pass sets up triple for Seminoles

videos.description: Terance Mann passes to Braian Angola in transition and he feeds it back to Mann who takes it to the rim for the flush with less than 5 minutes left in the game against the Buccaneers.
videos.headline: Mann assists and scores all night for Seminoles
